penilaianku diketahui.

79
00:06:06.189 --> 00:06:07.229
Kurasa

80
00:06:08.729 --> 00:06:09.899
aku tidak beruntung.

81
00:06:13.870 --> 00:06:14.870
Tidak.

82
00:06:16.740 --> 00:06:18.039
Kamu jahat.

